Axiom.name: Ax309
Axiom.text: ObjectProperty: <http://www.openaal.org/SAM/Ontology#has-coordinates> Annotations: comment "use this property to indicate than an entity has coordinates. To be useful the frame of reference for the coordinates has to be known to the user of the coordinates. Best practise is to use the same frame of reference for all coordinates that are used."^^string
